name: Coyote RIP
description:
My father told me it had been 20 years since coyotes don't show off in this region, till now, just to find out the people of the community had poisoned this lonely traveler, was heartbreaking for me, the little mountain name is San Antonio Coayuca, Axapusco, Estado de Mexico. means (place of coyotes) they have right to claim this place, so I made a graffiti protest to make conscious on people about these beings that they are not different from us, they are fighting every day to exist in this world, you can find it on my LostBoys Collection a 1/1 piece in Objekt.

Photo from 2016.

Another piece that was lost on my robbed computer.
